Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting Jinbe again at the Sea Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy learns about Fishman Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,along with Nami, Sanji, Chopper, Franky and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that we're like those stupid Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...to her hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:27.92,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Death of the Hero! A Shocking Truth of Tiger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:35.23,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,We finally got an Eternal Pose to Koala's hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:35.56,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}12 YEARS AGO - THE GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.20,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Nyu! Koala, you can go back to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my eyes. You've changed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:52.31,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}KOALA (THE FORMER SLAVE GIRL)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.94,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,You look like a girl now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't normally wear these...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We bought them for you but you don't like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your hair cut, too. Your mother will be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I should clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyu! You need to stop working when you don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not Mary Geoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.81,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,She needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:28.08,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}THE SHIP'S DOCTOR OF THE SUN PIRATES ALADDIN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:28.08,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Trauma can't be healed that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand her very well, Brother Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were a slave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't you rather kill her right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a human just like the one who owned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us the truth. What did your mother tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents looked down on Fishmen, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how human society is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They think that they're the best race in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Their children are spoiled by watching their example.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't stop until somebody destroys them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you guys have seen it enough while we were sailing these past 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Their disrespectful contemptuous look when they see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I would've done to them if the Boss wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was only a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--The others didn't look like that. --Brother Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everytime I see them, they all look terrified to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because we're pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so afraid of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't know you folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know someone, you naturally fear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only known the bad sort of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything about humans yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So getting to know someone would change something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyu. Hey, Koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess which hand it's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyu. Get it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Koala was fitting in so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when we arrived at Foolshout Island - where she came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:14.07,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}THE GRAND LINE - FOOLSHOUT ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:12.44,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Koala, get off of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.07,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,This is your home island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where is your home village? --Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'll walk you to the entrance to the village. --Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Koala! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good girl even though you're a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell everybody in the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...that there are so many good Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll grow up into a mean-spirited human like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Jinbe. You've changed a lot in last 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it. What's the point in her telling people that Fishmen are nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Otohime's speeches, her voice will just ring hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! Your daughter is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm so glad! --Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! She came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Koala? Koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the captain of the Sun Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fisher Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bad man, isn't he? Because he's a Fishman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been painful and hard being a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mom, not everybody was like the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Fishmen were all terrible but there were so many nice Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're only a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I know it because I was with Uncle Tiger and the others all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You would think so too if you'd lived with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for keeping your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget you - Uncle Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Hachi-san, Aladdin-san and all of the Sun Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to believe that when you grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,humans and Fishmen will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rear Admiral Strawberry from Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone on this island informed us of your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The elders of this village knew there might be trouble if we stopped you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but they approved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On the condition that we wouldn't repossess the girl who is the rightful property
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fisher Tiger, captain of the Sun Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are charged on two counts. I'm sure you know this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Assault and evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? I heard gunshots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the direction Boss headed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Navy! We're surrounded-choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat was a ploy to lure us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And Big Brother and all of us took it like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See?! That's what humans do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss Tai is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you handle this? We gotta go save the Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Brother Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to bring Big Brother back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong-san, this is not good! The ship is gonna be wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, get off of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hijack one of the Navy ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been shot so many times! Why is he still standing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you! I won't forgive you, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard something. Did you hear anything, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rear Admiral-dono! The Sun Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So that must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You all... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're responsible for all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I've done is for justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and to destroy the Sun Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead! I'd like to see you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to rescue Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and flee to sea with a Navy ship that Arlong stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean that you don't want a transfusion? Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost too much blood! You're gonna die if you don't get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boss' blood type is rare! No one in our crew has the same blood type!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood stock on this Navy ship must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But humans and we share the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can use human blood to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than live with their blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Their blood is filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They never stop disrespecting us Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna owe them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need mercy from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna give in to humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Was there something... between you and the humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna tell you this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On my last trip, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long trip, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you see during your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after I set off on my trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--I was caught. --What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent several years in Mary Geoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What I saw there was the insanity of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I fled for my life but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't just forget about all those slaves that I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I did things the way I wanted and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...I interfered with Queen Otohime as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody wants peace, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only people who can make a difference on that island...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...are children of the next generation like Koala who aren't prejudiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell the people on the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither the tragedy we endured nor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many humans who are compassionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's funny - the dying leave only their resentment behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though I know that there are kind humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a devil inside of me that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...clouding my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole body rejects their blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...accept humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Don't say such a thing and live! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! No matter what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the greatest benefactor to all the slaves who were freed by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hero to all Fishmen, who accomplished such a great feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to step further. You can't protect anybody with that punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is nobody else who wants to challenge me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become the leader of the Fishman District from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm your brother now, leave everything up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep my men safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--Boss! --Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fisher Tigers death sent ripples far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Fishmen and humans coexist, or must they remain separate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Fishmen waver, Arlong's hatred of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jinbe's desire to preserve Otohime and Tiger's ideals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,will bring their convictions into conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Sun Pirates Split! Jinbe vs Arlong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
